title: Hoops Tonight - LeBron James & Anthony Davis lack effort, Nets "fall apart" vs. Bucks
itunes:title: Hoops Tonight - LeBron James & Anthony Davis lack effort, Nets "fall apart" vs. Bucks
description:
First (3:00), Jason Timpf reacts to LeBron James, Anthony Davis, Russell Westbrook, and the Los Angeles Lakers' 110-99 loss to Nikola Jokic and the Denver Nuggets. What's wrong with LeBron and AD? Is Russell Westbrook's future with Los Angeles nearing its end? Later, (32:00) Jason Timpf reacts to Giannis Antetokounmpo and the Milwaukee Bucks' 110-99 win over Kevin Durant, Kyrie Irving, and the Brooklyn Nets. What makes Giannis so difficult to defend over a seven game series? And what changes do the Nets need to make if they want to reach the NBA Finals? #Volume #Herd

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
